query:
SELECT serve_date, p.food_id, query_line as "query_line!" FROM food_plan p NATURAL JOIN line l
                JOIN (SELECT food_id, (SELECT canteen_id FROM line WHERE line_id = query_line), query_line FROM UNNEST($1::uuid[], $2::uuid[]) x(food_id,query_line)) query 
                ON l.canteen_id = query.canteen_id AND p.food_id = query.food_id
            AND serve_date > NOW() - INTERVAL '3 months'
            ORDER BY serve_date ASC
